1
00:00:14,805 --> 00:00:20,243
<i>Connecting old words</i>
<i>that have been used up</i>

2
00:00:21,078 --> 00:00:28,985
<i>I just want to convey</i>
<i>my simple thoughts</i>

3
00:00:29,053 --> 00:00:34,423
<i>That day's faint wind blows away</i>

4
00:00:34,491 --> 00:00:38,552
<i>at the castle ruins of yesterday</i>

5
00:00:39,797 --> 00:00:44,700
<i>I'll laugh with you</i>
<i>and live for the moment</i>

6
00:00:45,436 --> 00:00:52,342
<i>Still that incident</i>
<i>will continue to trouble you, right?</i>

7
00:00:53,744 --> 00:00:57,236
<i>That's why it must be good bye</i>

8
00:00:57,314 --> 00:01:04,277
<i>Leaving nothing behind,</i>
<i>let us share what is left</i>

9
00:01:04,354 --> 00:01:11,419
<i>In time, we'll realize</i>
<i>that it was everything</i>

10
00:01:11,495 --> 00:01:18,162
<i>And sadness will touch our cheeks,</i>
<i>creating a river of tears</i>

11
00:01:18,569 --> 00:01:28,137
<i>Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex</i>
<i>and melting away</i>

12
00:01:30,992 --> 00:01:34,723
<i>Shikamaru always believed in me...</i>

13
00:01:35,597 --> 00:01:41,092
More than myself or Neji or
any of us here... He is stronger!

14
00:01:46,274 --> 00:01:47,571
Let's go, fatso!

15
00:01:49,010 --> 00:01:50,375
Don't YOU say that!

16
00:01:51,313 --> 00:01:53,406
Partial Expansion Jutsu...

17
00:01:55,150 --> 00:01:55,878
Arm!

18
00:02:02,691 --> 00:02:04,591
Partial Expansion Jutsu...

19
00:02:07,028 --> 00:02:07,926
Leg!

20
00:02:09,030 --> 00:02:10,622
Partial Expansion Jutsu...

21
00:02:10,699 --> 00:02:11,256
Arm!

22
00:02:25,947 --> 00:02:28,848
Don't mess with me! Scum!

23
00:02:32,420 --> 00:02:33,148
Eat this!

24
00:02:33,521 --> 00:02:34,112
What!

25
00:02:34,189 --> 00:02:36,453
Super Expansion Jutsu!

26
00:02:48,536 --> 00:02:54,406
<i>Good bye Old Friend!</i>
<i>I'll Always Believe in You!</i>

27
00:02:58,013 --> 00:03:00,481
<i>I did it... Shikamaru...</i>

28
00:03:05,186 --> 00:03:05,811
<i>What?!</i>

29
00:03:10,625 --> 00:03:13,025
I can't believe I had to get to
the second state

30
00:03:13,094 --> 00:03:15,824
for an opponent like this one...

31
00:03:19,968 --> 00:03:21,697
Slamming Palm

32
00:03:41,589 --> 00:03:44,114
<i>What... What is that appearance?!</i>

33
00:03:44,959 --> 00:03:47,257
Now that it's come to this, it's over.

34
00:03:47,729 --> 00:03:51,756
In the second state, I can put out ten times
more power than I have thus far.

35
00:03:51,833 --> 00:03:53,266
I'm invincible.

36
00:04:02,577 --> 00:04:04,477
<i>It's too painful to move...</i>

37
00:04:04,679 --> 00:04:07,978
<i>Who knew that the side effects</i>
<i>of the Curry Pill would be this intense.</i>

38
00:04:10,885 --> 00:04:14,753
This is what happens...

39
00:04:15,290 --> 00:04:18,623
to a powerless scum for butting in!

40
00:04:22,430 --> 00:04:27,424
Playing Ninja better suits you!

41
00:04:31,673 --> 00:04:35,165
<i>Raise your hand if you're playing Ninja.</i>

42
00:04:37,912 --> 00:04:39,140
Wait...

43
00:04:39,414 --> 00:04:41,405
Rock, paper... scissors!

44
00:04:42,283 --> 00:04:43,147
Split!

45
00:04:43,852 --> 00:04:46,980
One, two, three...

46
00:04:47,522 --> 00:04:49,752
W-Wait!

47
00:04:53,995 --> 00:04:56,691
99... 100!

48
00:05:03,004 --> 00:05:04,767
Hey! I said, split!

49
00:05:06,741 --> 00:05:07,673
Ouch!

50
00:05:08,176 --> 00:05:09,404
Found you!

51
00:05:10,111 --> 00:05:12,375
Give up quietly, the two of you!

52
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:21,515
We finally caught'em!

53
00:05:21,923 --> 00:05:26,257
I'm sick of this!
The team with Choji always loses!

54
00:05:27,695 --> 00:05:28,719
Sorry...

55
00:05:47,615 --> 00:05:51,244
I need a lot of Chakra
for this "second state."

56
00:05:51,586 --> 00:05:55,420
I'll take whatever Chakra
you have left!

57
00:05:56,658 --> 00:05:59,718
Well then, I'll take them now.

58
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,864
There's not much left...

59
00:06:07,936 --> 00:06:09,597
You're empty!

60
00:06:10,405 --> 00:06:13,397
I haven't had nearly enough to eat...

61
00:06:29,257 --> 00:06:31,953
I said I haven't had enough to eat!

62
00:06:33,595 --> 00:06:34,425
Huh?

63
00:06:34,896 --> 00:06:37,763
What, just one last piece, huh...

64
00:06:39,300 --> 00:06:42,531
When I said I haven't had
enough to eat...

65
00:06:46,374 --> 00:06:51,277
Just as I thought, you're the scum
used as a sacrificial pawn.

66
00:06:52,313 --> 00:06:57,046
Die... you pitiful fatso, the odd man out.

67
00:06:57,952 --> 00:07:00,648
<i>I won't let you play Ninja with us!</i>

68
00:07:01,389 --> 00:07:02,651
Why?

69
00:07:03,558 --> 00:07:06,026
Because if we let you play,
we'll lose.

70
00:07:06,194 --> 00:07:07,684
You're slow.

71
00:07:10,365 --> 00:07:14,301
Yeah, but... then the number
of people won't be even.

72
00:07:14,369 --> 00:07:17,770
Japanese chess is fun
because the number of pieces are even.

73
00:07:20,074 --> 00:07:23,840
A piece that is useless is
the same as not having that piece!

74
00:07:24,145 --> 00:07:25,305
Yeah, that's right!

75
00:07:28,549 --> 00:07:30,983
We're the ones with fewer people
and we're not complaining.

76
00:07:31,052 --> 00:07:32,246
Hurry up, let's do it!

77
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:34,886
If it's okay with you, then it's fine...

78
00:07:35,590 --> 00:07:36,784
Okay, it's settled!

79
00:07:36,858 --> 00:07:38,621
We can win it!

80
00:07:38,693 --> 00:07:39,125
Yes!

81
00:07:39,193 --> 00:07:41,127
Where are we gonna hide this time?

82
00:08:18,232 --> 00:08:22,635
And um, the whole Akimichi Clan
is fat and slow...

83
00:08:22,870 --> 00:08:25,065
That's what everyone says.

84
00:08:25,139 --> 00:08:26,197
Really...

85
00:08:30,211 --> 00:08:35,581
But Choji, you're a kindhearted guy...
more than everyone else.

86
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:43,152
One day, you'll surely make friends
who'll see that quality of yours.

87
00:08:44,892 --> 00:08:48,623
And then you should cherish
those friends

88
00:08:48,696 --> 00:08:51,256
and be the kind of friends
who believe in each other...

89
00:08:53,501 --> 00:08:58,700
<i>Can I really make... friends like that...</i>
<i>someone like me?</i>

90
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:01,169
Rest in peace...

91
00:09:01,242 --> 00:09:03,608
you're not the only one
I'm going to get.

92
00:09:04,379 --> 00:09:06,472
After I kill you,

93
00:09:06,547 --> 00:09:12,952
I'm going to get the cruel, sleazy,
mean guys who used you as a sacrifice!

94
00:09:20,194 --> 00:09:23,288
Because he... promised...

95
00:09:27,802 --> 00:09:30,635
<i>You better catch up with us... Choji.</i>

96
00:09:30,772 --> 00:09:31,864
<i>Okay!</i>

97
00:09:32,774 --> 00:09:38,542
He's definitely going to defeat
the opponent and come after us!

98
00:09:40,014 --> 00:09:40,605
Yep!

99
00:09:40,681 --> 00:09:44,412
That's right... he can do it.

100
00:09:46,754 --> 00:09:48,813
Okay! While I'm here...

101
00:09:50,091 --> 00:09:51,718
Me too...

102
00:09:55,730 --> 00:09:57,254
All right, everyone,

103
00:09:57,331 --> 00:10:00,198
we get Sasuke back
before Choji catches up!

104
00:10:01,936 --> 00:10:02,595
Wait!

105
00:10:04,005 --> 00:10:06,132
All right! Here we come!

106
00:10:20,154 --> 00:10:22,645
He's late... that Jirobo...

107
00:10:23,024 --> 00:10:25,424
He's greedy and eats so much...

108
00:10:25,927 --> 00:10:28,657
He's probably squeezing out Chakra
even from the marrow of their bones.

109
00:10:28,996 --> 00:10:31,692
I wish he had switched
with me already...

110
00:10:37,738 --> 00:10:40,366
Here, I'll give it back!

111
00:10:43,578 --> 00:10:44,704
Well, then...

112
00:10:44,879 --> 00:10:47,439
If I linger,
I won't be able to catch up.

113
00:10:47,982 --> 00:10:50,746
It's about time to put an end to this.

114
00:10:54,088 --> 00:10:57,080
<i>The Chili Pepper Pill is left...</i>

115
00:10:57,325 --> 00:11:03,753
<i>But... if I take that...</i>
<i>I'll die, without a doubt...</i>

116
00:11:08,769 --> 00:11:11,829
<i>Don't you dare die, Choji...</i>

117
00:11:16,511 --> 00:11:19,810
<i>We've been doing things together</i>
<i>since that day...</i>

118
00:11:41,102 --> 00:11:42,831
Oh! You...

119
00:11:44,071 --> 00:11:46,539
You... were there just now...

120
00:11:47,375 --> 00:11:48,967
What about playing Ninja?

121
00:11:49,744 --> 00:11:51,575
It was a drag,
so I pulled myself out from it.

122
00:11:51,646 --> 00:11:52,203
Huh?

123
00:11:52,647 --> 00:11:55,241
By the way, that's my special seat.

124
00:11:55,550 --> 00:11:56,983
Your special seat?

125
00:11:57,285 --> 00:12:02,382
I like to lie on my back and
look at the clouds on a nice day like this.

126
00:12:04,492 --> 00:12:06,289
You've come to look at clouds?

127
00:12:07,795 --> 00:12:09,763
Mind if I sit there?

128
00:12:10,231 --> 00:12:11,698
Oh... sure!

129
00:12:15,970 --> 00:12:19,303
This is a good place.
You can see the clouds well.

130
00:12:21,842 --> 00:12:22,536
Yeah...

131
00:12:26,981 --> 00:12:28,209
Why don't you...

132
00:12:28,282 --> 00:12:29,010
What?

133
00:12:30,851 --> 00:12:34,878
Watch the clouds with me
and lounge around?

134
00:12:36,624 --> 00:12:37,454
Okay!

135
00:12:38,359 --> 00:12:42,193
You know! I-I brought snacks.
Want some?

136
00:12:42,263 --> 00:12:43,423
Oh, that'd be great!

137
00:12:46,801 --> 00:12:47,597
Thanks.

138
00:12:52,006 --> 00:12:55,601
Eating potato chips
while watching clouds... this is the best.

139
00:12:55,977 --> 00:12:56,534
Yep!

140
00:13:01,248 --> 00:13:04,547
My name is Shikamaru...
from the Nara Clan.

141
00:13:04,986 --> 00:13:06,749
You... What's your name?

142
00:13:07,521 --> 00:13:11,514
It's Choji! Choji Akimichi
of the Akimichi Clan!

143
00:13:12,026 --> 00:13:15,621
Choji, huh...
I think I'll get along with you.

144
00:13:16,797 --> 00:13:17,957
Me, too!

145
00:13:28,275 --> 00:13:32,803
<i>We'll always do things together</i>
<i>from now on, too.</i>

146
00:13:34,949 --> 00:13:35,813
<i>Choji!</i>

147
00:13:45,793 --> 00:13:50,162
<i>Shikamaru... Sorry... I can't go...</i>

148
00:13:51,365 --> 00:13:53,629
It's over...

149
00:13:54,335 --> 00:13:55,996
<i>But, this guy...</i>

150
00:13:57,672 --> 00:14:00,539
<i>I have to beat him...</i>
<i>even if it means death.</i>

151
00:14:01,108 --> 00:14:03,736
No matter what you do now,
it's too late!

152
00:14:04,111 --> 00:14:04,941
Crushing Palm!

153
00:14:31,005 --> 00:14:33,235
<i>Wh-What's that...?</i>

154
00:14:35,076 --> 00:14:35,940
But...

155
00:14:37,044 --> 00:14:38,534
Boulder Blow!

156
00:14:41,182 --> 00:14:42,171
It's no good!

157
00:14:44,118 --> 00:14:47,451
I'm 100 times stronger than before!

158
00:14:54,862 --> 00:14:55,829
They say that food
can be a reason

159
00:14:55,896 --> 00:14:57,887
for people to hold a horrible grudge
against somebody.

160
00:14:58,299 --> 00:15:04,033
The blow just now...
was for eating the last bite of my snack...

161
00:15:04,672 --> 00:15:05,468
<i>No way!</i>

162
00:15:05,873 --> 00:15:09,206
<i>This guy has so much Chakra that</i>
<i>his body has changed physically!</i>

163
00:15:09,910 --> 00:15:11,468
And this is...

164
00:15:14,315 --> 00:15:18,274
for making fun of me by calling me
a sacrificial pawn and fat!

165
00:15:18,652 --> 00:15:21,917
But what I can't forgive you for
more than anything else...

166
00:15:23,491 --> 00:15:28,554
<i>You sure do suffer when</i>
<i>you have a stupid leader. You underlings!</i>

167
00:15:28,629 --> 00:15:30,961
<i>Well... I'll kill you losers</i>

168
00:15:31,031 --> 00:15:36,697
<i>before you suffer working</i>
<i>under a glum shadow lover like him!</i>

169
00:15:37,671 --> 00:15:41,300
<i>You should blame your stupid leader</i>
<i>for choosing you!</i>

170
00:15:43,511 --> 00:15:46,605
You insulted my best friend!

171
00:15:47,214 --> 00:15:53,050
More than mocking me
by calling me fat,

172
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:56,021
and poaching the last bite
of a four star meal...

173
00:15:57,958 --> 00:15:59,152
I can't forgive you for that!

174
00:16:01,929 --> 00:16:04,921
<i>All of my Chakra... to my left hand!</i>

175
00:16:05,332 --> 00:16:06,924
<i>Uh, uh oh!</i>

176
00:16:07,268 --> 00:16:11,068
This blow... is heavier than my life!

177
00:16:11,939 --> 00:16:14,499
W-Wait! Don't be hasty!

178
00:16:58,219 --> 00:16:59,413
I... I won.

179
00:17:00,487 --> 00:17:03,149
<i>Me... I won!</i>

180
00:17:28,148 --> 00:17:28,910
<i>Everyone...</i>

181
00:18:13,060 --> 00:18:14,687
<i>But Choji...</i>

182
00:18:15,362 --> 00:18:18,627
<i>you're a kindhearted guy,</i>
<i>more than everyone else...</i>

183
00:18:20,968 --> 00:18:26,338
<i>One day, you'll surely make friends</i>
<i>who'll see that part of you...</i>

184
00:18:28,309 --> 00:18:32,211
<i>And then you should cherish</i>
<i>those friends</i>

185
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:34,841
<i>and be the kind of friends</i>
<i>who believe in each other.</i>

186
00:18:50,464 --> 00:18:55,026
"Hurry up and get over here."
It's Naruto.

187
00:18:56,136 --> 00:18:58,764
"Everyone's waiting."
Kiba...

188
00:19:00,541 --> 00:19:02,008
Shikamaru...

189
00:19:17,124 --> 00:19:18,921
Ino Shika Cho!

190
00:19:33,741 --> 00:19:34,935
<i>Even if it is just potato chips,</i>

191
00:19:35,009 --> 00:19:38,069
<i>I won't let anybody else have</i>
<i>the last piece, no matter who you are.</i>

192
00:19:40,114 --> 00:19:43,606
<i>Choji and I have worked as a team</i>
<i>for many years,</i>

193
00:19:43,684 --> 00:19:46,152
<i>so coordinating with him</i>
<i>is easiest for me.</i>

194
00:19:53,794 --> 00:19:54,886
<i>Dad...</i>

195
00:19:55,896 --> 00:19:59,923
<i>I've made... a lot of friends...</i>

196
00:20:37,037 --> 00:20:37,765
What happened?

197
00:20:44,178 --> 00:20:44,974
Nothin'...

198
00:21:13,407 --> 00:21:20,506
<i>Once in a long while, once in a while</i>

199
00:21:20,647 --> 00:21:26,176
<i>The remnants of a person</i>
<i>broken by dreams</i>

200
00:21:26,353 --> 00:21:31,416
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

201
00:21:34,728 --> 00:21:41,725
<i>Clinging to the Divine,</i>
<i>clinging to Buddha</i>

202
00:21:41,802 --> 00:21:47,331
<i>The remnants of a person crying</i>

203
00:21:47,741 --> 00:21:51,302
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

204
00:21:52,980 --> 00:21:56,040
<i>Rendezvous with a happy dance circle</i>

205
00:21:56,116 --> 00:21:59,916
<i>This is my victory pose, round and around</i>
<i>(round around)</i>

206
00:22:00,254 --> 00:22:03,189
<i>Shake shake shake</i>
<i>Let's look</i>

207
00:22:03,257 --> 00:22:07,387
<i>With a bye bye rhythm that never ends</i>

208
00:22:16,570 --> 00:22:21,667
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

209
00:22:23,610 --> 00:22:26,875
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

210
00:22:27,281 --> 00:22:30,478
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

211
00:22:30,751 --> 00:22:34,744
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

212
00:22:39,526 --> 00:22:41,016
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

213
00:22:41,094 --> 00:22:42,061
Take this!

214
00:22:42,129 --> 00:22:43,118
Fang Over Fang!

215
00:22:44,031 --> 00:22:44,929
Byakugan!

216
00:22:46,533 --> 00:22:48,160
That damn spider bastard!

217
00:22:48,235 --> 00:22:51,329
Me, Naruto, Kiba and Neji.
Our careful planning is not working!

218
00:22:51,405 --> 00:22:54,033
If we dawdle Sasuke will be gone!

219
00:22:54,107 --> 00:22:55,472
Hey, what should we do?!

220
00:22:55,676 --> 00:22:58,907
If we want to continue our pursuit,
there's only one way to do it!

221
00:22:59,413 --> 00:23:02,576
Next time: "Your Opponent is Me!"
